comments: Gobert (UTA) initiates contact across Beal's (WAS) right arm that affects Beal's dunk attempt.
Gobert (UTA) extends his arms forward and marginal contact occurs with Gafford's (WAS) front as he secures the rebound.
Gafford (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Mitchell's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact.
Beal (WAS) moves laterally and delivers contact to Mitchell's (UTA) side that affects his SQBR.
Gobert (UTA) extends his left arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Gafford's (WAS) arms as he is passing.
O'Neale (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position when body contact occurs with Westbrook (WAS) as they come together during the drive.
Westbrook's (WAS) off-arm extends slightly against O'Neale's (UTA) front and marginal contact occurs as Westbrook releases away at the end of the drive.
Ingles (UTA) and Beal (WAS) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Beal (WAS) goes to, not through, Ingles' (UTA) space when marginal body contact occurs.
Bogdanovic (UTA) slightly extends his rear outward into Beal's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs as Beal goes over the screen.
Bonga (WAS) grasps and then quickly releases Bogdanovic's (UTA) arm during rebounding.
Hachimura (WAS) extends his forearm against Bogdanovic's (UTA) back and dislodges him from position during rebounding.
Mitchell (UTA) engages and disengages with Neto (WAS) during the inbound.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Neto (WAS).
O'Neale (UTA) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
Gobert (UTA) and Avdija (WAS) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Ingles (UTA) and Westbrook (WAS) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Beal's (WAS) right arm is extended forward when marginal contact occurs with Mitchell's (UTA) side as Mitchell changes direction after his gather.
Bertans (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact. Bertans and O'Neale then engage and disengage with one another after the initial contact.
Ingles (UTA) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
Neto (WAS) and O'Neale (UTA) engage and disengage with one another as the screen is set.
O'Neale (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Bonga's (WAS) path and absorbs the contact.
Beal (WAS) makes incidental contact with Mitchell (UTA) as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound. After communicating with the Replay Center, the on-court ruling of WAS ball was confirmed.
O'Neale (UTA) commits a take foul on Neto (WAS).
Mitchell's (UTA) off-arm extends toward Avdija's (WAS) side and marginal contact occurs as Mitchell changes direction.
Avdija (WAS) turns toward Mitchell (UTA) and marginal contact occurs with Mitchell's left arm after his gather.
